<paragraph blockId="7.[136,1452,265,544]" pageId="7" pageNumber="200">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[136,466,265,292]" pageId="7" pageNumber="200">Distribution and habitat:—</emphasis>
<taxonomicName authorityName="Boissier" authorityYear="1862" box="[466,692,266,292]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Euphorbiaceae" genus="Euphorbia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malpighiales" pageId="7" pageNumber="200" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="foliolosa">
<emphasis box="[466,692,266,292]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="200">Euphorbia foliolosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is endemic to 
<collectingCountry box="[859,927,266,292]" name="Brazil" pageId="7" pageNumber="200">Brazil</collectingCountry>
(
<collectingRegion box="[944,1059,266,292]" country="Brazil" name="Sao Paulo" pageId="7" pageNumber="200">São Paulo</collectingRegion>
and 
<collectingRegion box="[1115,1271,266,293]" country="Brazil" name="Minas Gerais" pageId="7" pageNumber="200">Minas Gerais</collectingRegion>
). In the State of 
<collectingRegion box="[136,249,302,328]" country="Brazil" name="Sao Paulo" pageId="7" pageNumber="200">São Paulo</collectingRegion>
the species occurs in cerrado vegetation.
</paragraph>
